sequenceDiagram
    participant ISS as Issuer
    participant UW as Underwriter /<br/>Primary Dealer
    participant INV as Investor
    participant CLEAR as Clearinghouse<br/>(FICC / DTC)
    participant CUST as Custodian
    participant PAY as Paying Agent

    Note over ISS,PAY: PHASE 1 - ISSUANCE (Primary Market)
    ISS->>UW: Mandate to issue / announce auction
    UW->>INV: Market bond (roadshow / WI trading)
    INV->>UW: Submit bids / IOIs
    UW->>ISS: Determine pricing (stop yield / spread)
    INV->>CLEAR: Settlement: cash delivered
    CLEAR->>CUST: Securities delivered (DVP)
    ISS-->>INV: Bond certificate (book-entry)

    Note over ISS,PAY: PHASE 2 - COUPON PAYMENTS (Semi-annual)
    loop Every 6 months
        ISS->>PAY: Transfer coupon funds
        PAY->>CUST: Distribute to holders of record
        CUST->>INV: Credit coupon to investor account
    end

    Note over ISS,PAY: PHASE 3 - SECONDARY TRADING
    INV->>UW: Request quote (RFQ)
    UW->>INV: Bid price: 98.25
    INV->>UW: Trade executed (sell at 98.25)
    UW->>CLEAR: Report trade
    CLEAR->>CUST: Settle T+1 (Treasuries) / T+2 (corporates)

    Note over ISS,PAY: PHASE 4 - MATURITY / REDEMPTION
    ISS->>PAY: Transfer principal + final coupon
    PAY->>CUST: Distribute to final holders
    CUST->>INV: Credit face value + final coupon
    Note over ISS: Bond retired / cancelled
